{"tid":736120,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有間「古天樂電影院」？　香港藝術中心戲院正式易命","createTime":"2018-07-10T04:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T08:15:32.000Z","uid":46435,"like":186,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"1238fedb1fa21cda9ae474731325a1eb66fdfe43","tid":736120,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"位於香港藝術中心，原先定名為「agnes b.」的電影院，由於贊助期完結，將由2018年7月19日起，由古天樂的電影公司天下一接手贊助，並正式命名為「古天樂電影院」（Louis Koo Cinema）。香港藝術中心更會聯同天下一電影於未來三年籌劃一系列「香港好電影」放映活動，當中所放映的電影由新一代本土導演、台前幕後及製作人等親自揀選，其範疇包括最期待搶先觀看的新導演作品，以及希望再次於大銀幕上欣賞的電影經典。<br />\n而首部於「古天樂電影院」放映的電影是陳詠燊首次執導，馬偉豪及廖婉虹監製，天下一投資，由黃修平導演所揀選其本年度最期待電影《逆流大叔》，非常有意義。<br />\n<br />\n古天樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31ae6370a1f22ef0b4b1d12cb65a6774300ab02","tid":736120,"uid":121473,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做實事為香港，古天樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffc30a8297aa6bf40cbcabc79acafb640caba9f","tid":736120,"uid":154684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:30:45.000Z","msg":"古生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fc4ea8685f750c87a6ecb0f1311486d3a1faaa","tid":736120,"uid":186882,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1